305
00:21:46,917 --> 00:21:48,750
<i>Kau tak tahu...</i>

306
00:21:50,542 --> 00:21:51,875
<i>di mana kau akan jatuh.</i>

307
00:21:53,625 --> 00:21:55,000
Lupakan itu sekarang.

308
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:01,708
Kalau tidak, kau akan berisiko

309
00:22:01,792 --> 00:22:04,042
