00:26:56,125 --> 00:26:57,667
Aku bingung harus mulai dari mana.

400
00:26:57,750 --> 00:27:00,333
Benito bertingkah...

401
00:27:01,042 --> 00:27:02,417
aneh belakangan ini, gugup...

402
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:04,708
<i>Antoñanzas tampak gelisah di rumah.</i>

403
00:27:04,792 --> 00:27:07,583
<i>Begitu gelisah</i>
<i>sehingga dia berenang saat dini hari</i>

404
00:27:07,667 --> 00:27:09,417
<i>dengan dua teman di kolam renang.</i>

405
00:27:10,417 --> 00:27:12,792
<i>Dan sepertinya dia mabuk.</i>

406
00:27:16,667 --> 00:27:19,875
<i>Kolonel, Sierra tak di rumah.</i>
<i>Dia pasti kabur.</i>

407
00:27:20,375 --> 00:27:21,958
Dasar jalang.

408
00:27:23,125 --> 00:27:26,625
