00:28:00,750 --> 00:28:01,583
Semuanya.

420
00:28:17,375 --> 00:28:18,458
Dengar, Amanda.

421
00:28:20,083 --> 00:28:21,542
Perbuatanmu tadi...

422
00:28:22,042 --> 00:28:24,875
