423
00:28:24,958 --> 00:28:27,708
- Aku tak mau dengar. Jangan ganggu aku.
- Begini...

424
00:28:27,792 --> 00:28:30,042
Kau dengar dia? Jangan ganggu dia.

425
00:28:30,125 --> 00:28:32,167
Apa aku harus mengusirmu dari sini?

426
00:28:32,250 --> 00:28:33,417
Apa yang kau lakukan?

427
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:35,833
Semuanya tenang, sekarang!

428
00:28:40,333 --> 00:28:43,375
Kau sungguh hina. Kau membuatku jijik.

429
00:28:43,458 --> 00:28:45,958
Kau menyebutku hina? Kau?

430
00:28:46,042 --> 00:28:47,125
Seorang bankir.

431
00:28:47,208 --> 00:28:50,292
Boneka sistem dan kapitalisme.

432
00:28:50,375 --> 00:28:53,250
Kau memberiku pelajaran etika?

433
00:28:53,333 --> 00:28:56,792
Seseorang yang tak berani
membela para karyawannya

434
00:28:56,875 --> 00:28:58,708
- dan melawan teroris.
- Diam!

435
00:29:00,583 --> 00:29:01,417
Tiarap!

436
00:29:01,833 --> 00:29:03,792
Tangan di kepala!

437
00:29:03,875 --> 00:29:05,500
Ayolah. Baiklah!

438
00:29:05,583 --> 00:29:06,667
Kau, di sana!

439
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:09,083
- Arturo!
